717690f-a.title: Manhattan: Broadway - 92nd Street
717690f-a.text:
Broadway, east side, from 92nd to 93rd Streets. These buildings
will be replaced by two fifteen-story apartment houses.
1921.
Coift of E. M. Jenks.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
